Bafana Bafana have been without a coach since December when Safa dismissed Ephraim Shakes Mashaba.Mashaba had directed rant at Safa officials and the media after the 2-1 win over Senegal in a 2018 World Cup qualifier in Polokwane on November 12. If negotiations between Safa and Baxter are successful and SuperSport United and Safa agree on an early termination of Baxter's current contract such appointment would only be effective at the end of the current PSL season officially commencing 1 July 2017.United are currently among the candidates for the Absa Premier League with Cape Town City Bidvest Wits Kaizer Chiefs and Mamelodi Sundowns. - TMG Digital/TMG Sport